| Context: To change a flat tire, start by loosening the lug nuts with the wrench while the car is on the ground. Place the jack under the vehicle frame and lift the car until the tire is off the ground. Remove the lug nuts completely and pull the flat tire off the hub. Mount the spare tire onto the hub and hand-tighten the lug nuts. Lower the car back to the ground and fully tighten the lug nuts in a star pattern. | Input: {"question": "What steps were taken?"} | Output: {"answer": ["loosening the lug nuts with the wrench while the car is on the ground", "Place the jack under the vehicle frame and lift the car until the tire is off the ground", "Remove the lug nuts completely and pull the flat tire off the hub", "Mount the spare tire onto the hub and hand-tighten the lug nuts", "Lower the car back to the ground and fully tighten the lug nuts in a star pattern"]}

