| Context: To plant a tree, dig a hole that is twice as wide as the root ball. Gently remove the sapling from its nursery container without damaging the roots. Place the tree in the center of the hole and ensure it stands straight. Backfill the hole with soil and tamp it down firmly to remove air pockets. Water the tree thoroughly and apply a layer of mulch around the base. | Input: {"question": "List the actions in order."} | Output: {"answer": ["dig a hole that is twice as wide as the root ball", "Gently remove the sapling from its nursery container without damaging the roots", "Place the tree in the center of the hole and ensure it stands straight", "Backfill the hole with soil and tamp it down firmly to remove air pockets", "Water the tree thoroughly and apply a layer of mulch around the base"]}

